<paragraph id="8BBEB10677DBFF20FF44A4D99525F875" blockId="140.[151,1436,1898,2031]" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">
<emphasis id="B9756D1477DBFF20FF44A4D99124F851" bold="true" box="[199,345,1970,1995]" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">Description.</emphasis>
Thin encrustation on a calcareous nodule (
<figureCitation id="133AAD8377DBFF20FCC8A4D993DDF851" box="[843,928,1970,1995]" captionStart="FIGURE 88" captionStartId="141.[151,250,1187,1209]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1166]" captionTargetId="figure@141.[151,1436,193,1166]" captionTargetPageId="141" captionText="FIGURE 88. Phorbas amaranthus Duchassaing &amp; Michelotti, 1864, a, habitus of RMNH Por. 10520 (scale bar = 1 cm), b – e, SEM images of spicules, b, large acanthostyle, b 1, detail of b, c, small acanthostyle, c 1, magnified image of c, d, tornote, d 1, details of d, e, arcuate isochela." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/273039/files/figure.png" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">Fig. 88</figureCitation>
a), red-brown in alcohol. Size 
<date id="FFBF97C677DBFF20FB7CA4D89559F850" box="[1279,1316,1971,1995]" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">2 x</date>
<quantity id="4CF91CE377DBFF20FAADA4D99501F850" box="[1326,1404,1970,1995]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="140" pageNumber="141" unit="cm" value="1.5">1.5 cm</quantity>
in lateral expansion, about 
<quantity id="4CF91CE377DBFF20FE2BA4BC9197F874" box="[424,490,2007,2031]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="140" pageNumber="141" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
in thickness. Surface faintly areolate, but no visible oscules. Consistency soft.
</paragraph>
<caption id="DF7EE18E77DAFF21FF14A7C891A8FB6C" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/273039/files/figure.png" pageId="141" pageNumber="142" targetBox="[151,1436,193,1166]" targetPageId="141">
